    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1DMPReinforcer" kindref="compound">DMPReinforcer</ref> provides a general framework for reinforcement learning. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It is an abstract class that implements elementary functionality that should be in common for all reinforcement learning methods (such as rollout execution). A concrete implementation of the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1DMPReinforcer" kindref="compound">DMPReinforcer</ref> has to implement the missing parts such as the methods getInitialRollout and computeRolloutParamters. </para>    </detaileddescription>
